summary: Moon & Myth Illustrations on Instagram: “🌙Day 29: Mary Wollstonecraft Shelley ⭐ I based my drawing of this amazing author off of...
title: Moon & Myth Illustrations on Instagram: “🌙Day 29: Mary Wollstonecraft Shelley ⭐ I based my drawing of this amazing author off of an old oil painting of her. I loved her crazy…”
excerpt: 103 Likes, 6 Comments - Moon & Myth Illustrations (@moonandmyth) on Instagram: “🌙Day 29: Mary Wollstonecraft Shelley ⭐ I based my drawing of this amazing author off of an old oil…”
description:
My recent illustration of Mary Shelley! I love her book Frankenstein, I just read a retelling of it called The Dark Descent of Elizabeth Frankenstein and really enjoyed it! It was a good retelling that still felt like its own story with nods to the original text. 

I used gouache and sakura pink copic pens to make this painting!
